description:
When I first met Julian I wasn’t really sure how well we were going to communicate. He was very shy and nervous, and he spoke quietly with a thick accent.

He’s a big, muscular guy at 6’4” tall. He has a very sexy Latin vibe about him.

“Where are you from?” I asked to break the ice.

“I was born in Argentina.”

Julian had just recently moved to the States and he was still perfecting his English.

“I like it very much here,” he said. “It is very different than back home!”

His favorite activity is soccer.

“I get aggressive when I play,” he said. “I sometimes have to calm myself down because I get so into it... I hate losing!”
title: Julian
